{
  "id": "crew-expense-precheck-gate",
  "name": "Expense Precheck Gate (no AI)",
  "category": "crews",
  "summary": "The crew loop with zero AI: a deterministic L1 policy assertion gates expense submissions. Watch rounds, verification, and terminal states \u2014 no API key needed.",
  "description": "A teaching crew that costs $0 and needs no credentials.\n\n1. Submit the hosted form (description + amount).\n2. The Policy Check runs an objective L1 assertion: {{$step.amount}} <= 500.\n3. Within policy -> the crew terminates 'success' on round 1. Over policy -> it retries once and stops as 'stalled', because a deterministic check can never improve.\n\nPress Run, open the form, and watch node statuses + the Logs panel in the editor.",
  "tags": [
    "crew",
    "form",
    "deterministic",
    "verified"
  ],
